{"tid":1045134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佐真奴創2332傳波0助攻紀錄","createTime":"2019-03-03T11:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T14:53:32.000Z","uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3766677f8383af75341c3c0f5e321c6b6a22308","tid":1045134,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"【資料庫】佐真奴創2332傳波0助攻紀錄<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=8d67c9f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】車路士中場佐真奴費路...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=24730983588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D24730983588&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=9121a24c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=24730983588</a><br />\n<br />\nNow 體育 - <a href=\"http://sports.now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=d46534ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sports.now.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=8d67c9f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】車路士中場佐真奴費路近日創了一大紀錄！據英國傳媒報道，這名意大利中場創出沒錄得1次助攻的傳球紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n車路士中場佐真奴費路（Jorginho）於去年夏天以5000萬鎊轉會費加盟，但加盟後一直未能適應英超的快速節奏。由於領隊沙利戰術上需要一名墮後中場，佐真奴常被委任正選，只是多以橫傳為主，不少網民都笑言他是「逗住型中場」，更被人笑他是沙利的親生兒子。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道便指佐真奴於車路士早前以2:0擊敗熱刺的英超上陣後，已經創下2332次傳球，但沒有任何1次助攻，這已較第2名史雲斯的里安比頓多次100次有多。<br />\n<br />\n不過現時還未肯定佐真奴於車路士的角色會否改變，在對熱刺一戰中，佐真奴於車路士只有52次傳球，比尼高路簡迪多兩次，但對比高華錫及馬高斯阿朗素都少，而且佐真奴有全場最高的4次攔截，似乎他將會參與更多防守。<br />\n<br />\n富咸VS車路士<br />\nNow621台03/03 22:05直播"},{"pid":"1250b26a86228b7c45074e45c24a366e41de74fe","tid":1045134,"uid":29993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"佐仔d傳波好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b966dcbc14b2a827fb060c6a36b6ea0f0a0944","tid":1045134,"uid":180178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"助功數唔重要 最緊要隊友踢得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef250f4f9aa8aca618e842ff6f4af16f92bdd467","tid":1045134,"uid":22832,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VxQ2G_-uJVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVxQ2G_-uJVc&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=61f4a845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VxQ2G_-uJVc</a>"},{"pid":"14b534ca46c22caf9fc1b72adc064998d07f4092","tid":1045134,"uid":22558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef250f4f9aa8aca618e842ff6f4af16f92bdd467","tid":1045134,"uid":22832,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VxQ2G_-uJVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVxQ2G_-uJVc&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=61f4a845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VxQ2G_-uJVc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"把握力好啲 佢都有幾個助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fa9750f70e5df33f29a90412a6a17bc731a13b","tid":1045134,"uid":181155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"好舒服 好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dcb3aad0165cdea921b5af8e4a7b35ba0ab6d0","tid":1045134,"uid":137467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl